== Loading REX file slices ==
 

*Open the file select browser as if you were going to open a regular audio file  (not patch)
[[Image:Redrum REX load.png|500px]]



*Select the REX file and click “Open”. The browser will now display a list of all the separate slices
*Select the desired slice and click open. The slices will now be loaded into the Redrum


